Fits a quantile regression to the data and draws the fitted quantiles with lines and then converts them with ggplotly








```{.bg-light}
m <-
  ggplot(mpg, aes(displ, 1 / hwy)) +
  geom_point()
p <-  m + geom_quantile()
```


```r
plotly::ggplotly(p)
```

```
## Smoothing formula not specified. Using: y ~ x
```
